HEADWORD: Cetyl
<hw>Ce"tyl</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ whale +
<ets>-yl</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A radical,
